verbose_text: In several animal knee OA models, IA Supartz FX suppressed collagenases (MMP-1, -3, and -13) and aggrecanase (ADAMTS5) gene expressions, prevented chondrocyte apoptosis, decreased the number of Caspase-3 and Fas positive cells, and suppressed the decrease of pyridinoline (a protective, naturally occurring collagen cross-linker) in cartilage.
